intertrust.modules.ag.generic

Class MappingPolicyAspects

  • java.lang.Object
    • intertrust.modules.ag.generic.MappingPolicyAspects

  • public class MappingPolicyAspects
extends java.lang.Object
    This component represents a mapping table (ListAF and MappingSCA) with the information needed to relate the different security policies of an application with the aspects that need to be dynamically incorporated to the application in order to satisfy each negotiated security policy.
    Author:
    UMA
